MARCI: It was 1942, and Susi
Penzias had fled Nazi Germany.

01:16:40.610 --> 01:16:43.540 align:middle line:84%
She was in Italy
trying to hide away.

01:16:43.540 --> 01:16:46.200 align:middle line:84%
And she was taking
a train ride one day

01:16:46.200 --> 01:16:50.640 align:middle line:84%
when all of a sudden, two
police officers came on board.

01:16:50.640 --> 01:16:55.100 align:middle line:84%
And they were dressed in the
government Fascisti uniforms.

01:16:55.100 --> 01:16:57.620 align:middle line:84%
And they were on board
going passenger by passenger

01:16:57.620 --> 01:17:00.045 align:middle line:90%
to inspect everyone's papers.

01:17:00.045 --> 01:17:01.527 align:middle line:84%
Well, Susi knew
exactly what was going

01:17:01.527 --> 01:17:02.560 align:middle line:90%
to happen when they got to her.

01:17:02.560 --> 01:17:04.280 align:middle line:84%
She didn't have any
papers, and they

01:17:04.280 --> 01:17:06.140 align:middle line:84%
were going to find
here and send her

01:17:06.140 --> 01:17:10.460 align:middle line:84%
