camps to certainly her death.

01:17:10.460 --> 01:17:15.940 align:middle line:84%
And as they got closer, Susi
started trembling and sobbing.

01:17:15.940 --> 01:17:18.930 align:middle line:84%
And the stranger sitting next to
her on the train looked at her

01:17:18.930 --> 01:17:20.080 align:middle line:90%
and said, what's wrong?

01:17:20.080 --> 01:17:21.560 align:middle line:90%
Why are you crying?

01:17:21.560 --> 01:17:23.755 align:middle line:84%
And she whispered
to him, I'm Jewish

01:17:23.755 --> 01:17:27.230 align:middle line:90%
and I don't have any papers.

01:17:27.230 --> 01:17:31.250 align:middle line:84%
He paused for a few seconds,
and then he yelled at her.

01:17:31.250 --> 01:17:32.470 align:middle line:90%
You idiot.

01:17:32.470 --> 01:17:33.610 align:middle line:90%
You imbecile.

01:17:33.610 --> 01:17:35.140 align:middle line:90%
I can't believe you did that.

01:17:35.140 --> 01:17:37.490 align:middle line:90%
How stupid of you.

01:17:37.490 --> 01:17:40.760 align:middle line:84%
She was shocked, and she
began sobbing even more.

01:17:40.760 --> 01:17:42.940 align:middle line:84%
And at this commotion,
the two police officers

01:17:42.940 --> 01:17:45.920 align:middle line:84%
came over to them and
said, what's going on here?

01:17:45.920 --> 01:17:47.395 align:middle line:84%
And the man looked up
at the police officers

01:17:47.395 --> 01:17:50.690 align:middle line:84%
and said, officers,
take this woman away.

01:17:50.690 --> 01:17:52.370 align:middle line:84%
My wife, she's
forgotten her papers.

01:17:52.370 --> 01:17:53.070 align:middle line:90%
I can't believe it.

01:17:53.070 --> 01:17:55.230 align:middle line:84%
I have my papers, but
she's forgotten hers.

01:17:55.230 --> 01:17:57.470 align:middle line:84%
She always forgets everything.
I'm sick of her.

01:17:57.470 --> 01:17:59.740 align:middle line:90%
Take her away.

01:17:59.740 --> 01:18:02.220 align:middle line:84%
And at that, the
police officers just

01:18:02.220 --> 01:18:07.370 align:middle line:84%
