spat and moved on past them.

01:18:07.370 --> 01:18:14.700 align:middle line:84%
In one courageous act, that
stranger saved Susi's life.

01:18:14.700 --> 01:18:17.150 align:middle line:90%
Susi never saw that man again.

01:18:17.150 --> 01:18:19.890 align:middle line:90%
She never even knew his name.

01:18:19.890 --> 01:18:24.520 align:middle line:84%
The greatest people in
life are not necessarily

01:18:24.520 --> 01:18:29.010 align:middle line:84%
those who are creating
huge businesses,

01:18:29.010 --> 01:18:31.940 align:middle line:84%
